oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Spring Opening Festival at Monroe's Bluegrass Musicland Park (16432)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Bluegrass music; Jim and Jesse; Martin, Jimmy; Monroe, James; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color half sheet (red and black on white) announcing the Spring Opening Festival featuring James Monroe, Jim and Jesse, Jimmy Martin, and others at Monroe's Bluegrass Musicland Park on May 9, 10, and 11. Poster features metal photoplates of James Monroe, Jim and Jesse, and Jimmy Martin. To view the paperwork associated with this poster, see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/34156.
